long_description: rehabone healthcare was started in the year 2015 by experienced professionals dealing with physiotherapy and rehabilitation medicine with the intention to provide affordable high quality healthcare to masses in around bangalore. the founder and director rehab one healthcare, dr m.prasanna who worked more than 20 years in this field with experience of academic, research and clinical practice. rehabone healthcare committed to work on evidence based practice with the motto of adding life to years. currently rehab one operates in three location such as banaswadi, kr puram and t.c palya providing physiotherapy services and later plans to expand throughout bangalore. we have well established spacious department with state of art facility, rehab one provides range of services in orthopaedic , neurology , paediatric ,geriatric and sports physiotherapy. we have well qualified and experienced doctors with masters degree in various specialties who handle patients effectively. we are providing service in our out patient department and wards in attached hospital.
